author: djames
msg: Cleanup leftover Ruby test repositories and working copies before
running each individual unit test in the Ruby test suite. Because we
can now guarantee that each unit test starts with a fresh checkout
and a fresh working copy, the Ruby test suite will be easier to debug.
This patch is a followup to r15112.
(setup_basic): Remove old working copies before checking out a new
(setup_repository): Remove old repositories before creating a new
Instead, the Ruby test suite will cleanup the Ruby test repositories
and working copies prior to each unit test.
